name: Unidentified_rebel_corporal
content: A human individual served as a corporal in the Alliance to Restore the Republic during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, the corporal was part of the Eleventh Division that traveled to the planet Ab Dalis following the scattering of the rebel fleet after the Battle of Hoth. Sometime after the division arrived at Ab Dalis, they were found by the assault group of Imperial Commander Ellian Zahra who sent the Star Destroyer Ultima II commanded by Admiral Kalaxo to destroy the Eleventh Division. Colonel Chouch of the Eleventh Division had the corporal send out a message requesting aid for the division from any rebel forces, which was received by Starlight Squadron, who responded to the call and arrived to assist them. The corporal later sent the coordinates of a mountain, in reality a dormant volcano, that the Ultima II was stationed above to the squadron. Starlight Squadron fired on the mountain, and it erupted, destroying the Star Destroyer.
